OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FAirlines are asking the government to
OL,8,Fintervene to cushion the blow from the
OL,9,Feconomic fallout in the Middle East,
OL,10,Fin order to protect business travel,
OL,11,Fholiday traffic and freight
OL,12,Foperations, ITV News understands.
OL,14,FOngoing war in the Gulf and the
OL,15,Fclosure of the Strait of Hormuz, a
OL,16,Fvital shipping route for oil and gas,
OL,17,Fhave caused the price of refined
OL,18,Fproducts like jet fuel to surge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
