CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791154
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FITV News has seen a confidential
OL,8,Fbriefing document submitted to
OL,9,Fministers and the regulator, the Civil
OL,10,FAviation Authority (CAA), warning that
OL,11,Fif the disruption "continues or
OL,12,Fworsens", it will force airlines to
OL,13,Fcut flights and push up fares.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791154
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FIn the document, Airlines UK, which
OL,8,Frepresents a number of carriers,
OL,9,Fincluding British Airways, easyJet,
OL,10,FJet2, Loganair, Ryanair, TUI, UPS and
OL,11,FVirgin Atlantic, says "the doubling of
OL,12,Fjet fuel costs (with fuel accounting
OL,13,Ffor around one-third of airline costs)
OL,14,Frepresents a major additional price
OL,15,Fshock".
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FAirlines want the government to step
OL,8,Fin to secure fuel supplies, cut taxes
OL,9,Fon tickets and give them more
OL,10,Fflexibility to cope with soaring costs
OL,11,Fand potential compensation claims.
OL,13,FThe document calls on the government
OL,14,Fto consider:
OL,16,FLast week, the head of the
OL,17,FInternational Energy Agency warned
OL,18,Fthat Europe has "maybe six weeks of
OL,19,Fjet fuel left" before airlines would
OL,20,Fneed to start making cuts to their
OL,21,Fsummer schedules.
OL,26,@zD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FTalks between airlines, airports, the
OL,8,FDepartment for Transport and the CAA
OL,9,Fhave been ongoing since the crisis
OL,10,Fbegan.
OL,12,FIEA Executive Director Fatih Birol
OL,13,Fsaid last week that Europe has "maybe
OL,14,Fsix weeks or so (of) jet fuel left"
OL,16,FOne source close to the negotiations
OL,17,Ftold ITV News there is a need for the
OL,18,Fgovernment to be more decisive, and
OL,19,Fthat some of the requests airlines are
OL,20,Fmaking are simply common sense.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"The agreement at the moment allows
OL,8,Fslot alleviation at the point there's
OL,9,Fno fuel, by which time it's too late,"
OL,10,Fthey said.
OL,12,F"The government doesn't get it.
OL,13,FOfficials are seeking 100% clarity,
OL,14,Fbut airlines and airports need action
OL,15,Fnow. Slot alleviation and temporary
OL,16,Fpermission for the use of Jet A fuel -
OL,17,Fthese are decisions that are in the
OL,18,Fconsumer interest".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FThere is broad agreement that aviation
OL,8,Fis highly exposed to the aftershocks
OL,9,Fof higher energy prices, but even
OL,10,Fwithin the industry there is
OL,11,Fdisagreement about how the government
OL,12,Fshould respond.
OL,14,F"If the government triggers slot
OL,15,Falleviation, airlines will cancel
OL,16,Fflights and the financial pressure
OL,17,Fwill be transferred onto airports,"
OL,18,Fanother source told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"Airfares are rising, but at the
OL,8,Fmoment there's no problem with
OL,9,Fsupplies. The airlines are chancing
OL,10,Fit. When I see a plane with no fuel,
OL,11,Fthen I'll have sympathy."
OL,13,FIran effectively closed the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz to shipping seven weeks ago in
OL,15,Fresponse to US and Israeli attacks,
OL,16,Fand it remains shut despite a flurry
OL,17,Fof contradictory announcements over
OL,18,Fthe weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FSupplies of oil, gas and their
OL,8,Fderivatives are tightening. A scramble
OL,9,Ffor stocks is underway, and the
OL,10,Fconsequences for airlines and
OL,11,Fpassengers, could escalate quickly.
OL,13,FAirlines UK told ITV News: "Airlines
OL,14,Fcontinue to operate normally and are
OL,15,Fnot experiencing issues with jet fuel
OL,16,Fsupply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"As you would expect we remain in
OL,8,Fclose contact with the DfT.
OL,9,FAuthorities including in the UK have
OL,10,Fprovided alleviation from slot rules
OL,11,Fin the past when geopolitical events
OL,12,Fhave affected the aviation industry.
OL,14,F"Additional flexibility, should it be
OL,15,Fneeded, would enable airlines to
OL,16,Foperate most efficiently to minimise
OL,17,Fany disruption to customers and
OL,18,Fmaintain long established global
OL,19,Fnetworks."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FThe Department of Transport said: "UK
OL,8,Fairlines are clear that they are
OL,9,Fcurrently not seeing a shortage of jet
OL,10,Ffuel.
OL,12,F"We continue to work with fuel
OL,13,Fsuppliers, airlines and international
OL,14,Fcounterparts on our contingency
OL,15,Fplanning, to ensure people keep moving
OL,16,Fand businesses are supported while the
OL,17,Fconflict is ongoing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776791155
OL,3,CAirlines call for emergency government
OL,4,Csupport as war hits airfares and
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"Our overriding priority is to de-
OL,8,Fescalate this conflict, open up the
OL,9,FStrait and prevent disruption to
OL,10,Fpassengers."
OL,12,FITV News has approached Airports UK,
OL,13,Fthe Civil Aviation Authority, and the
OL,14,FDepartment for Energy and Net Zero for
OL,15,Fcomment.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
